               <scopecontent id="aspace_8619163d77fc8cfae52f6ec58669807d">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The play was developed as an independent study project by Michael Leibenluft and written and developed by Andrew Chittenden, Kelsey Clark, Cory Finley, Peregrine Heard, Emily Hoffman, Cordelia Istel, Sophia Janowitz, Michael Leibenluft, Jacob Liberman, and Liz Mandeville in 2009.  In 2010 the play was adapted to film.</p>
